metadata.name: Frozen sunrise
metadata.description:
Frozen winds are rolling in from the ocean with a new fresh scent, feeling your mind wake up from the depths of dark city life. As the sun lights up sky it marks the beginning of a new chapter of hope, a deeper connection. May the light guide your path along your journey forward, breathe, let it go, release what holding you back and keep it moving. You will attract bonds and connections that bring out the best in you, make you feel loved, worthy, appreciated and secure.  
----  
Ni'a I want to thank, for all the inspiration this one is for you. I felt something i never felt.
